                            Game Day Phase 2: &quot;. . . And Then I Saw The Light&quot;
                        </div>
                    

                    
                        <div id="breadcrumbs">
                            <a href="/gamedayindex">Game Day</a> &raquo; <a href="/gamedaypart2index">Game Day, Phase 2: Contain</a> &raquo; Game Day Phase 2: &quot;. . . And Then I Saw The Light&quot;
